title: Lenovo Ideacentre 510S First Look! - CES 2016
description:
If you're looking into upgrading your current machine to something light and sleek. The Lenovo Ideacentre 510S All-In-One desktop is the right machine for you. Running an i7 6th Gen Processor, 16GBs of memory and you are able to get this machine with NVIDIA GT 930A graphic processor. With all these specs you are able to take care of business and do some PC gaming on the side.
